 :EndIf
 ‚ćĚ Wall avoidance ‚ÄĒ steer toward centre when near edges
 margin‚Üźr√ó15
 nearWall‚Üź(x<margin)‚ą®(x>(w-margin))‚ą®(y<margin)‚ą®(y>(h-margin))
 :If nearWall
